This was the work of the caleño who identified the corpse of Alfonso Cano
A lofoscopista of Cali went down in history as the man who confirmed the death of "Alfonso Cano".
The work of these officers is key.
On November 4 a lofoscopista of the CTI in Cali went down in history as the man who confirmed the identity of the maximum Chief of the Farc: "Alfonso Cano", through the comparison of their fingerprints.
Of the seven lofoscopistas working in the branch of the CTI, this week played "availability" question time Eliazar González, a man of Puerto Tejada, who has 21 years working in the area of judicial investigation.
At the start of his career, Gonzalez worked in municipalities of Chocó, where he often had to go for more than five days in the jungle to reach the site where they were the bodies which should be identified.
In 2000 he moved to the capital of the Valley and, after conducting the relevant courses, specialized in lofoscopia, which is the study of skin friction, IE, palms of the hands and feet.
The week of the operation against alias Alfonso Cano to Eliazar they warned him to take minimum clothes for three days.
Something big was waiting for him.
The Friday night came out to the Cauca in a helicopter from Palmyra.
I knew that it should identify two corpses and that it suspected that one of them was the man heading the oldest guerrilla movement in the world, by what he asked him to take card decadactilar of Guillermo León Sáenz (his real name).
However, when she arrived with the research team to the site in which the corpse was not recognized by their physical appearance, as it was very different from who he had seen in the media.
It was without beard, dressed as a farmer in the area, without glasses and much thinner.
But fingerprints do not lie.
Accompanied by a magnifying glass galtoniana, ink, a transplantador and a flashlight, Eliazar compared the fingerprints of the corpse with the card.
His eye not failed him: was "Alfonso Cano".
That same night, a native man of Puerto Tejada was commissioned to confirm him to the Minister of Defense, Juan Carlos Pinzon, yes it was the maximum head of the Farc.
In search of the footprint
For a dactiloscopista of the Sijín of Cali recognition made by President Juan Manuel Santos Eliazar González, at the press conference by the operation against "Cano", is very significant.
Many people don't know our work.
The dactiloscopistas is an exact science, no margin of error, which can be key in solving crimes.
Apart from the identification of corpses, the lofoscopistas support research for offences such as theft and homicide and confirmed the identity of the persons captured.
When they are caught, many criminals present false certificates or have no papers.
We take them the fingerprint printing and look for them in the database.
The investigator told that in a case of theft, fell it to remove a piece of wall of a House, because there the thief had supported his hand to get a safe deposit box full of jewels and money.
"Walls are difficult because they are not areas appropriate to get a fingerprint printing but then could obtain the footprint of the hand and identify the offender, who had participated in different thefts," he recalled.
Fingerprints can also discard or reaffirm suspects in homicide cases.
Recently found a dead man, with bottles of liquor to her around.
Through research, it was determined that a family member might be suspect of the crime and, indeed, a mark on the bottle coincided.
Although this does not guarantee that it has been the killer, yes locates it at the scene of the crime.
A dactiloscopista of the CTI explained that in objects "fingerprints are drawn with chemical reagents or physicists".
When they appear, a transplantador is used or tape to lift them.
After this, the prints are sent Asif, which is the criminal database, or the Registrar.
"The problem is that there are still many undocumented Colombians", said the expert of CTI.
He clarified that not everything is as shown in the CSI television show.
Just as not everything that glitters is gold, not everything that touches becomes footprint.
However, if it can be used, if the respective matching is performed.
